BIOGRAPHIES OF AUTHORS
Bunari Bunari is a Doctoral (Dr) and Lecturer in Department of History Education, Faculty of Education and Teacher Training, Universitas Riau, Pekanbaru, Indonesia. His research focuses on history and education sociology. He can be contacted at email: bunari@lecturer.unri.ac.id.
Johan Setiawan is a Doctoral (Dr) and Lecturer in Department of History Education, Faculty of Education and Teacher Training, Universitas Muhammadiyah Metro, Indonesia. He completed the Master (M.Pd.) and Doctoral Program (Dr.) at Graduate School, Yogyakarta State University. His research focuses on history education, character education, and Indonesian history. He can be contacted at email: johansetiawan767@gmail.com, johansetiawan@ummetro.ac.id.
Muhammad Anas Ma’arif is Lecturer in Department of Islamic Religious Education Program, Tarbiyah Faculty, Institut Pesantren K.H. Abdul Chalim Pacet Mojokerto, Mojokerto, Indonesia. His research focuses on Teacher Education, Peace Education, Educational Leadership, and Islamic Education. He can be contacted at email: anasmaarif@ikhac.ac.id.
Reski Purnamasari is Lecturer in Department of Sociology Education, Faculty of Teacher Training and Education, Universitas Lambung Mangkurat, Indonesia. His research focuses on educational sociology and sociology of religion. She can be contacted at email: reski@ulm.ac.id.
Hadisaputra Hadisaputra is a Lecturer in Department of Sociology Education, Faculty of Teacher Training and Education, Universitas Muhammadiyah Makassar. His research focuses on educational sociology, sociology of religion, and political sociology. He can be contacted at email: hadisaputra@unismuh.ac.id.
Sudirman Sudirman is a Doctoral (Dr) and Lecturer in Department of Pancasila and Citizenship Education, STKIP Yayasan Abdi Pendidikan Payakumbuh, Indonesia. His research focuses on social science and Citizenship Education. He can be contacted at email: dirmanaalim66@gmail.com.